com.kontakt.sdk.ble.data

Enum IBeaconService

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<IBeaconService>
      • com.kontakt.sdk.ble.data.IBeaconService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<IBeaconService>

    public enum IBeaconService
extends Enum<IBeaconService>
    Service Model describes service propagated by kontakt.io beacon after connecting to it. For more information refer to kontakt.io Beacon specification - version 2.0.
    See Also:
    kontakt.io Beacon Datasheet - version 2.0.
